content: I'm thinking of pairing them with dresses and skirts, maybe even a flowy maxi dress for a more bohemian look. I've also been considering getting a pair of high-waisted mom jeans to pair with the boots for a more casual, everyday look. Speaking of jeans, I recently exchanged a pair of distressed denim jeans from American Eagle for a pair of high-waisted mom jeans, and I've been loving them!
